<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>せんせい箱・まなび箱 | 先生と子どもの毎日をちょっと楽にするアプリ集</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+JP:wght@400;500;700;800&family=Inter:wght@500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Rounded:opsz,wght,FILL,GRAD@24,500,1,0" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="index.css">
</head>
<body>
    <header class="site-header">
        <div class="header-inner">
            <h1><span class="material-symbols-rounded">inventory_2</span>せんせい箱・まなび箱</h1>
            <p>先生と子どもの毎日をちょっと楽にするアプリ集</p>
        </div>
    </header>

    <nav class="tab-nav" aria-label="カテゴリ">
        <button class="tab-button active" type="button" data-target="tab-class">
            <span class="material-symbols-rounded">groups</span>
            <span>授業・学級</span>
        </button>
        <button class="tab-button" type="button" data-target="tab-office">
            <span class="material-symbols-rounded">edit_note</span>
            <span>所見・事務</span>
        </button>
        <button class="tab-button" type="button" data-target="tab-learning">
            <span class="material-symbols-rounded">school</span>
            <span>まなび箱</span>
        </button>
        <button class="tab-button" type="button" data-target="tab-info">
            <span class="material-symbols-rounded">campaign</span>
            <span>情報・連絡</span>
        </button>
    </nav>

    <main class="page">
        <section class="about-panel" aria-labelledby="about-title">
            <h2 id="about-title">せんせい箱・まなび箱とは</h2>
            <p>このサイト「せんせい箱・まなび箱」は、小学校・中学校の先生が授業や学級活動、校務で使える便利なアプリと、子どもの学びに役立つツールをまとめたポータルサイトです。</p>
            <p>学級活動で使えるタイマーやくじ、クイズ、通知表の記載文例づくり、ファイル整理やPDF変換など、現場で役立つツールを無料で公開しています。</p>
            <p>授業中にすぐ使いたいとき、学級活動でさっと開きたいとき、校務の合間に短時間で処理したいときに役立つように、シンプルで使いやすい形にしています。</p>
        </section>

        <div class="search-area">
            <span class="material-symbols-rounded" aria-hidden="true">search</span>
            <input id="search-input" type="search" placeholder="アプリを検索（例：くじ、タイマー、所見、九九、PDF）" autocomplete="off">
        </div>

        <section id="tab-class" class="tab-panel active" aria-labelledby="tab-class-title">
            <div class="section-heading">
                <span class="material-symbols-rounded">groups</span>
                <h2 id="tab-class-title">授業・学級で使う</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="app-grid" id="class-apps-container"></div>
        </section>

        <section id="tab-office" class="tab-panel" aria-labelledby="tab-office-title">
            <div class="section-heading">
                <span class="material-symbols-rounded">edit_note</span>
                <h2 id="tab-office-title">所見・校務で使う</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="app-grid" id="office-apps-container"></div>
        </section>

        <section id="tab-learning" class="tab-panel" aria-labelledby="tab-learning-title">
            <div class="learning-portal">
                <div class="learning-nav">
                    <a class="learning-brand" href="https://sites.google.com/view/manabinohako/home" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">まなび箱</a>
                    <div class="learning-links" aria-label="まなび箱メニュー">
                        <a href="https://sites.google.com/view/manabinohako/home" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Home</a>
                        <button type="button" data-target="tab-class">せんせい箱</button>
                        <a href="#song-section">歌でおぼえよう♪</a>
                        <a href="#science-section">理科ページ</a>
                        <span class="material-symbols-rounded" aria-hidden="true">search</span>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="learning-hero" aria-labelledby="tab-learning-title">
                    <span class="hero-item hero-book material-symbols-rounded" aria-hidden="true">menu_book</span>
                    <span class="hero-item hero-music material-symbols-rounded" aria-hidden="true">music_note</span>
                    <span class="hero-item hero-science material-symbols-rounded" aria-hidden="true">science</span>
                    <span class="hero-item hero-light material-symbols-rounded" aria-hidden="true">emoji_objects</span>
                    <span class="hero-item hero-globe material-symbols-rounded" aria-hidden="true">public</span>
                    <span class="hero-item hero-pencil material-symbols-rounded" aria-hidden="true">edit</span>
                    <div class="hero-cloud">
                        <h2 id="tab-learning-title">まなび箱</h2>
                        <p>楽しく学べる 学習ポータル</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="learning-band">
                    <h3>小学生向け</h3>
                </div>

                <div class="grade-grid" id="learning-apps-container"></div>

                <div class="learning-tool-section" id="song-section">
                    <div class="section-heading">
                        <span class="material-symbols-rounded">auto_stories</span>
                        <h2>学習ツール</h2>
                    </div>
                    <div class="app-grid" id="learning-tools-container"></div>
                </div>

                <div id="science-section" class="learning-note">
                    <span class="material-symbols-rounded">science</span>
                    <div>
                        <h3>理科ページ</h3>
                        <p>理科の学習リンクや実験動画などを、ここに追加できます。</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="tab-info" class="tab-panel" aria-labelledby="tab-info-title">
            <div class="section-heading">
                <span class="material-symbols-rounded">campaign</span>
                <h2 id="tab-info-title">情報・連絡</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="info-list" id="info-apps-container"></div>
        </section>

        <p class="empty-message" id="empty-message">該当するアプリが見つかりませんでした。</p>

        <footer class="site-footer">
            <section>
                <h2>このサイトについて</h2>
                <p>先生の授業・学級経営・校務をサポートするための無料Webアプリ集です。すべてブラウザで利用でき、インストール不要で手軽に使えます。</p>
            </section>
            <section>
                <h2>プライバシーポリシー</h2>
                <p>当サイトではGoogle AdSenseを利用する場合があります。広告配信事業者は、ユーザーの興味に応じた広告を表示するためCookieを使用することがあります。</p>
            </section>
            <section>
                <h2>利用規約</h2>
                <p>当サイトの内容は教育活動の補助を目的として提供しています。利用は自己責任でお願いいたします。</p>
            </section>
        </footer>
    </main>

    <script src="app-data.js"></script>
    <script>
        const containers = {
            "class-apps": document.getElementById("class-apps-container"),
            "office-apps": document.getElementById("office-apps-container"),
            "learning-apps": document.getElementById("learning-apps-container"),
            "learning-tools": document.getElementById("learning-tools-container"),
            "info-apps": document.getElementById("info-apps-container")
        };

        function cardTarget(app) {
            return app.isExternal ? ' target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"' : "";
        }

        function renderCards() {
            containers["class-apps"].innerHTML = appData["class-apps"].map(app => `
                <a class="app-card" href="${app.link}"${cardTarget(app)}>
                    <span class="icon-circle tone-${app.tone || "blue"} material-symbols-rounded">${app.icon}</span>
                    <span class="card-title">${app.title}</span>
                    <span class="card-desc">${app.desc}</span>
                </a>
            `).join("");

            containers["office-apps"].innerHTML = appData["office-apps"].map(app => `
                <a class="app-card" href="${app.link}"${cardTarget(app)}>
                    <span class="icon-circle tone-${app.tone || "blue"} material-symbols-rounded">${app.icon}</span>
                    <span class="card-title">${app.title}</span>
                    <span class="card-desc">${app.desc}</span>
                </a>
            `).join("");

            containers["learning-apps"].innerHTML = appData["learning-grades"].map(app => `
                <a class="grade-card grade-${app.grade}" href="${app.link}"${cardTarget(app)}>
                    <span class="grade-number">${app.grade}</span>
                    <span class="grade-title">${app.title}</span>
                </a>
            `).join("");

            containers["learning-tools"].innerHTML = appData["learning-apps"].map(app => `
                <a class="app-card" href="${app.link}"${cardTarget(app)}>
                    <span class="icon-circle tone-${app.tone || "blue"} material-symbols-rounded">${app.icon}</span>
                    <span class="card-title">${app.title}</span>
                    <span class="card-desc">${app.desc}</span>
                </a>
            `).join("");

            containers["info-apps"].innerHTML = appData["info-apps"].map(app => `
                <a class="info-card" href="${app.link}"${cardTarget(app)}>
                    <span class="info-icon ${app.iconClass || ""} tone-${app.tone || "blue"} material-symbols-rounded">${app.icon}</span>
                    <span class="info-body">
                        <span class="card-title">${app.title}</span>
                        <span class="card-desc">${app.desc.replace(/\n/g, "<br>")}</span>
                    </span>
                </a>
            `).join("");
        }

        function switchTab(targetId) {
            document.querySelectorAll(".tab-button").forEach(button => {
                button.classList.toggle("active", button.dataset.target === targetId);
            });
            document.querySelectorAll(".tab-panel").forEach(panel => {
                panel.classList.toggle("active", panel.id === targetId);
            });
            document.body.classList.toggle("learning-mode", targetId === "tab-learning");
            if (targetId === "tab-learning") {
                document.getElementById("search-input").value = "";
            }
            applySearch();
        }

        function applySearch() {
            const term = document.getElementById("search-input").value.trim().toLowerCase();
            const activePanel = document.querySelector(".tab-panel.active");
            const cards = activePanel.querySelectorAll(".app-card, .info-card, .grade-card");
            let visibleCount = 0;

            cards.forEach(card => {
                const matched = !term || card.textContent.toLowerCase().includes(term);
                card.hidden = !matched;
                if (matched) visibleCount += 1;
            });

            document.getElementById("empty-message").classList.toggle("show", visibleCount === 0);
        }

        document.querySelectorAll(".tab-button, .learning-links button[data-target]").forEach(button => {
            button.addEventListener("click", () => switchTab(button.dataset.target));
        });

        document.getElementById("search-input").addEventListener("input", applySearch);

        renderCards();
    </script>
</body>
</html>
